comment: Stop-antistop (sbottom-antisbottom) production cross sections for the stop (sbottom) pair production model with the resto of squarks and gluino decoupled. Provided by the authors of NNLL-fast (arXiv:1607.07741), including the combined scale and PDF+AlphaS uncertainties. The PDF set used for the calculations is NNLO PDF4LHC21 Hessian (LHAPDF ID 93300), and renormalization scale is set equal to factorization scale.
